# DRIFT.AI Backend Environment Variables

# Supabase PostgreSQL Connection String (Transaction mode URI)
# 1. Go to your Supabase Project Dashboard
# 2. Settings -> Database
# 3. Scroll to "Connection string" -> URI
# 4. Replace [YOUR-PASSWORD] and paste it below:
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres.xxx:YOUR-PASSWORD@aws-0-us-east-1.pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres
